OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPound hits new 37-year low 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas retail sales slide      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The pound has fallen to a new 37-year  
OL,6, low against the US dollar after figures
OL,7, showed UK retail sales fell sharply in 
OL,8, August as the rise in the cost of      
OL,9, living continued to hit households.    
OL,11,FThe larger-than-expected drop in sales 
OL,12,Fof 1.6% prompted fresh concerns over   
OL,13,Fthe state of the country's economy.    
OL,15,FSales in across all retail sectors fell
OL,16,Fin August as households cut back in the
OL,17,Fface of rising prices.                 
OL,19,FSome analysts suggested retail figures 
OL,20,Fshowed the UK is already in recession. 
